          "التوبة": "Tawbah — repentance, turning back to God",
          "شعبان": "Sha'ban — the eighth month of the Islamic calendar, preceding Ramadan",
          "الصراط": "al-Sirat — the bridge over Hellfire that all must cross on the Day of Judgment",
          "دار القرار": "Dar al-Qarar — the Abode of Permanence, a Quranic designation for Paradise"
        },
        "seo_question": "What supplication did Imam al-Rida recommend for the month of Sha'ban?"
      },
      "ur": {
